1. Install OpenNI-Compliant Sensor Driver v5.1.6.6

http://www.openni.org/openni-sdk/openni-sdk-history-2/
http://www.openni.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Sensor-Bin-Linux-x64-v5.1.6.6.tar.zip

2. Launch the OpenNi driver

$ roslaunch openni_launch openni.launch

Note: if the driver does not load properly, unplug the camera, run the driver, plug in the camera.

3. Check to make sure the camera is working:

$ rosrun image_view image_view image:=/camera/rgb/image_color

4. Launch ar_kinect

$ roslaunch ar_kinect ar_kinect.launch

5. Run rviz

$ rosrun rviz rviz

Load the ar_kinect.rviz configuration

